QRCodeHelper
============

QRCode Helper plugin


Example
=======

1. install
./script/plugin install git://github.com/nog/qrcode_helper.git

2. in your view

<%=qrcode_image_tag(text, size, options) %>
text:qrcode data
size:qrcode side size
options: options of image_tag method.


